<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="101" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d101">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source"><persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_CC2" type="to">Churchill</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d101fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché London, via
                                Navy channels.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-08">8 November 1943</date>.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Number 411, personal and secret, for the <gloss target="#t_FormerNavalPerson1">Former Naval Person</gloss> from the
                            President.</p>
                        <p>Your 479.<note n="2" xml:id="d101fn2"><hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_54">p. 54</ref>.</note> I have not received
                            invitation from <persName corresp="#p_KAC1">Kirk</persName> and have
                            directed my representative <persName corresp="#p_RMF1">Reilly</persName>
                            to make arrangements after consultation with British Minister.<note n="3" xml:id="d101fn3"><persName corresp="#p_CRG1">Richard
                                    Casey</persName>, Minister of State Resident in the Middle East
                                (at Cairo).</note></p>
                        <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_RFD1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>